    </h2>

    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-slate-500 font-medium mb-10"
    >
      <div
        class="problem-item flex items-center gap-3 bg-white px-5 py-3 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
      >
